Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.22,0:00:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is locked! Why is the door locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we prisoners or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahjumma, just hit me instead like earlier. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Episode 4{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for many reasons. You even got hit because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom is severely wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Different than her daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At least she gave us blankets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Are you really going to sleep here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we say, my mom will never open the door for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Tak! Chief Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a door there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked... That one might be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get out from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should I dig a tunnel with a spoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I should! Just go over there, you're disrupting me.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous. Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About the baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You had the chance to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wanted to tell you, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bring myself to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Um. You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a "seaweed ear," would you like some?\N(part of the seaweed at the root that's not common)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"A seaweed ear?" Why is there an ear on seaweed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had anything to eat yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually people get angrier when they're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little to get rid of your hunger for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, forget it. How can I eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even so... I can't ignore your sincerity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of taste is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, in this country village there isn't any...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's edible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm eating it because it's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm forcibly eating it to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to live a long, long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, you're not a picky eater.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd be picky about everything since you're from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right. It's not like I'm Tarzan of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In this sort of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating this sort of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to live a long life. Ugh, it tastes so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a cochlea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a fish eyeball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really chewy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I pull out the other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hates skipping meals the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can drop off food, \N(something done in prison)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,at least make some rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't die from skipping one meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the storage room is full of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,lock me in with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, do you like our Mi Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'd rather prefer the oldest sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that... it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, you frustrating fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to lock them up together so they can either become attached or detached,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,a decision will be made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at him from before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he hates her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really. This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think anyone would like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably couldn't even give it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish Box? What's a Wish Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, give it!\N -Wait, wait. Let me read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be something amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's really not interesting, I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He really can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me read it to see how amazing it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I hope my friend can{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}return the stuff she borrowed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you ask your friend to give back the things she borrowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your friend have something on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.88,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she couldn't give it back because she lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't put her in a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} If I do an errand, I wish my friends would{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tell me "thank you," even just once.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have some sort of trauma when you were little?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a serious disease, a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you they were boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One more. Last, last. Last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I hope Dad{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} went somewhere nice in Heaven.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When did your father pass away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to go out on boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed him so I put this in the Wish Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're similar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was young, my father
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and mother also passed away from a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's only right that I go to the hospital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um... \N-You already have a girlfriend that you want to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Realistically, we won't be able to raise this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I raise him on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,even after you two are married,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you will still be concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This baby will become
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a burden to you and your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to give the baby
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a life without blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young... \NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.36,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my mistake for going to the wrong room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, let's go to the hospital together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to take responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still don't want to let a girl go through something so hard alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N-Lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And... don't refuse, because I'm going to go to the hospital with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you go by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night. \N-Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I think it is really fascinating that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we've met 4 times, and we've slept together 2 of the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That connection between people is really{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hard to understand.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we met in a good situation,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess we would call it {\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}destiny.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ Even a bad fate may turn to love. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ Shout and call out.♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ I only love you.♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ My heart wants you, you who is like fate. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ I love you. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosquitoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill all of you! All the mosquitoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to the hospital.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't have to worry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will cheer up.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to wake you up just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where... where is the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Obstetrics, obstetrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What about obstetrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl! These two were playing with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she is going to get an abortion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will happen if we go after her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to break her legs if something were to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So where is this? Quickly! Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think the first ship has already left. What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? We have to make a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? There is nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.21,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she answering the call or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young isn't picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be causing trouble for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going to have to make a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship, ship, ship, ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Isn't that President Choi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We are coming, we are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is working without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming, coming, just wait a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Obstetrics{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it done yet? How much longer do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on a rotation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Give me a notice when it is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.70,0:15:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you. What did you come here for again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that, that surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the person from the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, how are we going to find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that there are three hospitals here in total, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,One on the three way road, one next to the market, and one downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to break into groups to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young's mother with the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you two, since you guys are always scheming things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamo-hamo~~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We will go from the farthest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone finds her, call everyone, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see you, I tell you horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be sorry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I did was listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the one who is going through a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But how come you are here, Priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the person I wanted to meet is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is more nerve wracking than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:17:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You look nice even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to cheer you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but there is nothing I can tell you except for you to rethink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It is something you can't have back even if you regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pray with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pray?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I get confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying is all about the heart, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just need to talk comfortably, like you talked to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young! Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take pity on{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the baby that met a{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}very, very bad mother.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let it go to a wonderful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For not being able to protect this baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very, very sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved that I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be nervous and strengthen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♫ When I open my eyes ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ let me hear it. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♫ the words of "I love you", my melody. ♫{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO! CEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young. Kim Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.82,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I'm looking for a patient named Kim Mi Young. She has big eyes and pale skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking for her so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You are going to have the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, a girl shouldn't come to a place like this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? It hurt a lot, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, okay? \N -You're really sorry? We're really over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've found her. Kim Mi Young is in consultation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to relax. I will take care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.77,0:21:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to see it well because it's still early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the baby right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.38,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at it right now, the baby is about 0.2 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,0.2...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,0.2 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much smaller than you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fetus can understand everything the parents say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:22:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.69,0:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.96,0:22:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the Mother and Child's Health Act, Article 14,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you and the baby's father are allowing me to conduct an induced abortion operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.72,0:22:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as you were impregnated while you were unconscious due to alcohol or sleeping medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.03,0:22:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a consent form for the surgery. You just have to sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a life form of its own.{\b1\i1}This child will become{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a burden to you and your future wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got fingers and toes. He's got everything.{\b1\i1}To the baby,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.38,0:24:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't want to give him a life without blessings.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.35,0:24:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, peekaboo. Peakboo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.19,0:24:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What... Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you going?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry and relax. I'm going to put you\N under general anesthesia now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.87,0:25:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't! Kim Mi Young, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.84,0:25:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Hurry and take this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.11,0:25:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.99,0:26:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.22,0:26:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After hearing the heartbeat, 9 out of 10 can't go through with the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.94,0:26:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.21,0:26:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.61,0:26:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But what are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.79,0:26:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.05,0:26:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.79,0:26:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Do you know what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.76,0:26:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah wait. Let's talk about this. Do you know how tough it was for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.63,0:26:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this something we can solve by talking?\N What happened? What about the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.74,0:26:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You! How could you not even stop her? Do you still call yourself a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.71,0:27:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah really!\N- Oh, it's the Chairwoman's car!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.11,0:27:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the Chairwoman's car!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.45,0:27:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.59,0:27:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how cruel you are! You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.49,0:27:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.97,0:27:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This grandma of yours... My neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.54,0:27:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.17,0:27:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, listen to me first, please! Everyone, just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.71,0:27:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma! Mi Young's mother!\N -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.75,0:27:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby... The baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.79,0:27:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is fine. It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.92,0:27:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby is alright.\N- Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.69,0:27:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Kim Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:28:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have made a selfish decision. I hope you will agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.34,0:28:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.77,0:28:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.94,0:28:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.91,0:28:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? "I will," what? Tell us what you are thinking comfortably as if you are at home. "I will," what? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.05,0:28:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We will have this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.89,0:28:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairwoman, Chairwoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.43,0:28:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aigoo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.40,0:28:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, you will marry our Mi Young?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that..!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.47,0:28:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does it become that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.71,0:28:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant that I will have the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.31,0:28:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything regarding Kim Mi Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.68,0:28:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I can't marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.32,0:28:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You won't marry her but you want the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:29:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see our Mi Young as nothing but a surrogate mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.09,0:29:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your words are rather harsh. What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.10,0:29:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After she gives birth to the baby, I will guarantee a new start to her life with exceptional treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.84,0:29:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Tak. Ah, ow, ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.31,0:29:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, what a shameless punk. You want her to be a surrogate...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.21,0:29:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Who do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.51,0:29:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aiyoo. We don't think of you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.95,0:29:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In my eyes, you're our in-laws and Mi Young is my granddaughter-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.46,0:29:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I see the baby as my great-grandchild.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.16,0:29:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided. I will definitely get them married.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.97,0:29:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me what you think. I heard the blabber that he said, but
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.70,0:29:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you must have something in mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.97,0:29:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I think it's practically impossible for us to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.58,0:30:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What..? Are you in your right mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.05,0:30:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We conceived this baby by mistake, not out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.09,0:30:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage should happen out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.56,0:30:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That is exactly what I'm trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.17,0:30:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.27,0:30:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Shut up! How dare you..{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.54,0:30:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.44,0:30:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more to say here, especially when the person involved is coming out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.21,0:30:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,End of discussion. Take your irresponsible grandson and leave from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.82,0:30:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will deal with my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.42,0:30:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, aigoo, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.32,0:30:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young is now my granddaughter-in-law, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.69,0:30:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Hold on! Sister-in law...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.56,0:30:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,just say you'll get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.66,0:30:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, Chairwoman...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.00,0:30:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't my sister-in-law marry your grandson, and we'll become in-laws afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.47,0:30:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why don't you cut our factory some slack?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.91,0:31:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll starve to death without the soap factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.41,0:31:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Young, please save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.02,0:31:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mi Young, we beg of you. You just need to make up your mind.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.99,0:31:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! What kind of embarrassment is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.99,0:31:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we sold our factory and land, we have never sold our souls before!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.26,0:31:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand still if you try to cling onto them one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.10,0:31:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,President Park, you have a boat at least, so you have something to lean on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have nothing if we lose the factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.07,0:31:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Mi Young, please think this through.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.07,0:31:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Our lives are in your hands.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.74,0:31:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I told you to stop! {\i} Are you not listening to me, now that the factory is bankrupt?! Is that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.11,0:31:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you like this so suddenly, President?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.18,0:31:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We should at least hold on to our pride to live!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.55,0:31:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.79,0:31:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} What are you guys doing with my daughter?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.09,0:31:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She, as you can see, is not pretty nor does she have a great body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.00,0:31:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, was she smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.80,0:32:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she did poorly in school as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.87,0:32:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, why are you saying such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.81,0:32:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She was always last in math, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.31,0:32:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's lacking in so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.08,0:32:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,instead she is also a child that can never be calculative in her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.18,0:32:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though her room is a mess because she can't throw things away (sentimental),
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.09,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,instead she can't also ever throw away (ignore) a person's feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.52,0:32:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she doesn't listen to her mother when I tell her countless times to please live more shrewdly,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.73,0:32:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,she's a child that can never refuse the request of a complete stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.23,0:32:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...to our Mi Young, who is like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.74,0:32:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,how dare you pressure her like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.97,0:32:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Who are you all?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.84,0:32:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to tell her what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.01,0:32:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you ask this so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.42,0:33:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Marriage is like an eternal promise.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.29,0:33:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} We don't know each other well enough to make such a commitment.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.40,0:33:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we say that we can have the baby, marriage is a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you with your senseless talk. Your stomach is so full it's about to burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.44,0:33:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what you're saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.14,0:33:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One! You are going to have this baby and give it up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.84,0:33:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll become a woman that has a past.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.98,0:34:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Two! You are going to have this baby and raise him/her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.62,0:34:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All you are going to be is a single mom.{\b1\i1} -That's right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.89,0:34:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.93,0:34:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true but how bewildered must that other person be?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's right to force him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.47,0:34:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you, I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.37,0:34:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.37,0:34:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that he pulled you out of the operating room?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.71,0:34:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, he has some conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.75,0:34:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Think through this carefully. It's not like there is no father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.12,0:34:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby's dad is alive and well. Why in the world would you have this baby as a single mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.02,0:34:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your own selfishness. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.13,0:34:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kim Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.44,0:34:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,come see me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.37,0:35:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.34,0:35:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man. I bet he'll be amazing as a husband if they get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have no intentions of marrying me at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.27,0:35:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a great person, Gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.04,0:35:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I believe you'd be a great dad to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.34,0:35:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.48,0:35:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how much you love that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go through with this marriage if it's going to make someone unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.59,0:35:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already lost
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my qualification as a man to Se Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.80,0:36:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And although it was our mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.20,0:36:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that the baby in your stomach is our child
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.14,0:36:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will not ever change.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.91,0:36:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already the bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.42,0:36:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a great dad to the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.66,0:36:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.83,0:36:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Se Ra is still the only one for me right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.43,0:36:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't guarantee how much
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.37,0:36:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and when my heart will move towards you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.08,0:36:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but I will promise you this one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.36,0:37:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,At least to our baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.13,0:37:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a great dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.60,0:37:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can accept this,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.61,0:37:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.74,0:37:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.65,0:37:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.42,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,want to be a great mom to this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.00,0:37:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.32,0:38:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Help out over here, please!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.82,0:38:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Hello! {\i} \N Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.89,0:38:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! You look so handsome! {\b1\i1} Come over here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.66,0:38:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always looked like a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.37,0:38:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Please clear this over here!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.77,0:38:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook! You're here! Today you went for a red fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.44,0:38:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With the elders of both families...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.74,0:38:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's done getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.98,0:38:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.42,0:38:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.59,0:38:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.79,0:38:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, getting married today is a little too fast, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.30,0:38:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you want to wait until your belly is as big as a mountain to go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:39:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I know buying things together as newlyweds and going on a honeymoon is part of the fun in getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.58,0:39:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but what can you do? What's done is already done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.14,0:39:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They can have the baby, we can reserve a banquet hall
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.88,0:39:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and have a stunning wedding one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.25,0:39:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt bad that I wasn't able to prepare a dowry because it was so last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.36,0:39:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't we prepare everything then, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.76,0:39:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What dowry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The best dowry has already been prepared right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.68,0:39:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.69,0:39:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} My Gun.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.43,0:40:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.33,0:40:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.70,0:40:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really Gun? It's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.67,0:40:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.14,0:40:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Don't hang up, you can't hang up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.21,0:40:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra! Where are you going? We're going to start soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.49,0:40:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Se Ra..{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.69,0:40:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.96,0:40:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually have something to say to you..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you know how long I've been waiting for you to call?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.16,0:40:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.23,0:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know how painful it was to wait like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.60,0:40:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.47,0:40:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wronged you greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.81,0:40:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you've wronged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.58,0:40:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, as a human being you've made me wait too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.45,0:40:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you had every right to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.62,0:41:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't do this again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.49,0:41:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the proposal turning out like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.63,0:41:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.84,0:41:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.34,0:41:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even more sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.34,0:41:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're calling it even, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.54,0:41:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're letting this go completely, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.88,0:41:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There's no one but you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.78,0:41:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You called exactly at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.02,0:41:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.42,0:41:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like someone's looking for you. Is something going on today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.92,0:41:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's my first performance as the prima ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.09,0:41:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The first day I stand on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.73,0:41:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.60,0:41:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} To be honest, I was a bit worried I might mess up because I was so nervous.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.50,0:41:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I've heard your voice, I think I can do well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.31,0:41:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.65,0:42:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Se Ra, there's no time. Everyone's waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.58,0:42:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gun, thank you for calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.42,0:42:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.05,0:42:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Se...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.23,0:42:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Se Ra..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.87,0:42:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Here comes the groom!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.81,0:42:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.11,0:42:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's handsome!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.92,0:42:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Brother-in-law! You look so handsome!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.95,0:42:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Brother-in-law!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.02,0:42:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's really handsome.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.83,0:42:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Here comes the bride!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.94,0:43:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty! Wow!{\b1\i1} She's so pretty!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.27,0:43:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's beautiful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.31,0:43:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a goddess!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.01,0:43:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Cute! You're really pretty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.09,0:43:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Beautiful!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.39,0:43:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Now, the bride and groom will exchange their vows.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.50,0:43:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you the bride, Kim Mi Young,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.27,0:43:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}promise to take Lee Gun as your lawfully wedded husband,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.27,0:43:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through happiness, sickness, and loneliness,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.74,0:43:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} and to love him unconditionally{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.28,0:43:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} without change?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.12,0:43:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.95,0:43:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Do you, husband, Lee Gun, promise this as well?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.70,0:44:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come now, come now...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.00,0:44:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your voice is too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.44,0:44:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.85,0:44:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He's answered 'Yes', everyone you've heard his answer!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.12,0:44:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.79,0:44:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.76,0:44:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there will be the exchange of the rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.00,0:44:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what your father wore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.77,0:44:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I had no idea you'd be my life.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.14,0:44:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ For when I looked into your eyes, I knew someday you'd be my wife.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.72,0:45:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I know there's times when I am wrong.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.26,0:45:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.17,0:45:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Ring! \N - I did well, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.37,0:45:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} This is a proposal ring!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.10,0:45:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} It can't be worn by another woman first! It'll bring bad luck!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.81,0:45:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ You took my heart so unexpectedly.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.62,0:45:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Applause! \N♬ I knew that you would be the one.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.52,0:45:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ I always knew that there was something special about you♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.76,0:45:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♬ the day that you walked into my life.♬{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.67,0:45:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay here for a couple of nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.07,0:45:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of all the company matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.64,0:46:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. Take him with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.48,0:46:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like he runs a small corner store. He's in charge of a huge enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.48,0:46:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand that much. It was an unexpected marriage, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.09,0:46:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Son-in-law Lee,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.26,0:46:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what'll happen if you wrong our Mi Young, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.06,0:46:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be the rice scoop, but a baseball bat that'll fly your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.27,0:46:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.74,0:46:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then my granddaughter-in-law, you stay here with your mom for a couple of days before you come.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.12,0:46:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom must be sad to send off her youngest daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.55,0:46:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prepare a beautiful newlywed's room in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.42,0:46:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's alright, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.52,0:46:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, then I will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.89,0:46:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay~
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.79,0:46:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then..
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.76,0:46:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Have a safe trip back.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.30,0:47:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.34,0:47:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.74,0:47:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} CEO!!!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.54,0:47:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Oh my.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.65,0:47:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aigoo, aigoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.98,0:47:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.92,0:47:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO, I'm really thankful that you have accepted all the factory workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.99,0:47:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,so I prepared this amazing gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.43,0:47:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the men in your family
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.80,0:47:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are lacking a bit in stamina. So, that's why you're the 9th generation of the only sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.40,0:47:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of nonsense are you spouting?! Our family is not just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.24,0:47:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're above normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.84,0:47:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then from now on, you will be above normal and become the greatest in Korea!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.84,0:47:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you have this!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.65,0:47:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.15,0:47:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it when you get to Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.89,0:47:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to brag or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.39,0:47:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm the best contributor to this wedding, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.06,0:48:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our island's finest selection at the same level as our famous soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.80,0:48:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have developed this ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.97,0:48:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. This is what brought
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.07,0:48:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you and our sister-in-law together. \N - Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.90,0:48:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say anymore. Hurry and get on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.21,0:48:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairwoman is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.04,0:48:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Chief Secretary Tak? Not taking care of his CEO...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.81,0:48:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.31,0:48:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew the sea that you look upon from a dock would look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.89,0:48:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything with the word "Jang" added to it is sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.16,0:48:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Station (like a bus station), airport, dock,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.29,0:48:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.13,0:48:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook, I don't know when it'll be,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.50,0:48:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but be well until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.74,0:48:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Chief Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.54,0:48:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi Sook!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.65,0:48:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Chief Secretary Tak!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.75,0:48:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Chief Secretary, yes! (I hear you calling my name)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.08,0:49:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.32,0:49:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.05,0:49:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold it. She wants us to say our goodbyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.15,0:49:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.76,0:49:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.16,0:49:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.36,0:49:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Be well, Mi Sook!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.70,0:49:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother-in-law! Have a safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.81,0:49:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.81,0:49:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Timing and Subtitles brought to you by The Fated Team @ Viki{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.45,0:49:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Kim Hee Won{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.59,0:49:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your name was Kim Mi Young when you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.53,0:49:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember that clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.86,0:49:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My older brother used to call out, "Mi Young, Mi Young."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.27,0:49:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, by any chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.57,0:49:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,remember this photo? It was at the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.98,0:50:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell from this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.28,0:50:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a memory of going to the zoo with my older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.62,0:50:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you have a scar from a fire, is it ok for me to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.96,0:50:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how you got the scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.40,0:50:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I think it was when I was 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.80,0:50:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The kettle on the heater in the orphanage fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.57,0:50:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister got the scar when she was 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.91,0:50:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you were my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.42,0:50:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oppa...\N- Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.19,0:50:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How is our baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.83,0:50:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.40,0:51:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For not being able to protect this baby,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.24,0:51:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm really, really sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.01,0:51:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.66,0:51:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Star, I can see a star, Chief Secretary Tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.43,0:51:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife is looking at you from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.57,0:51:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.41,0:51:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.91,0:51:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.25,0:51:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,CEO,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.28,0:51:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because it wasn't Miss Se Ra but Mi Young,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.49,0:51:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.26,0:52:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad that the CEO who is 9th generation's only son,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.03,0:52:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,got not only a wife, but a child, like a 1+1 deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.43,0:52:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.17,0:52:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.11,0:52:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma is happy, and Mi Young's mother is happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.11,0:52:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak is happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.08,0:52:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.65,0:52:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can only laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.69,0:52:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Only laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.56,0:52:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, but... (suddenly speaking in lower terms)
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.76,0:52:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "hey".
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.87,0:52:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But what about Mrs. Mi Young attracted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.90,0:52:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She is very different from Miss Se Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.61,0:52:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like a wide variety of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.21,0:53:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak, what do you mean by attracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.25,0:53:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Attracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.89,0:53:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.16,0:53:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to open this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.43,0:53:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,President Park told you to open it when you get to Seoul.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.87,0:53:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak can have it. I hate him so much that I can't stand a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.01,0:53:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.22,0:53:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength, strength "Joagra".
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.15,0:53:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.15,0:53:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with one gulp you will become
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.56,0:53:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the Superman of the night. \N- Superman!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.53,0:53:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go around Hong Kong 3 times in one night and 24 hours isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.60,0:53:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A super stimulant for
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.40,0:53:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,those who are afraid of the night. \NIt says it is a stimulant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.94,0:53:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Stimulant?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.15,0:54:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is our Island's specialty.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.38,0:54:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We, two, invented it ourselves!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.65,0:54:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You, and my sister-in-law...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.16,0:54:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't say it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.89,0:54:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drink, Drink!\N- Health tonic, health tonic.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.40,0:54:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It stimulates me?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.63,0:54:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, good. Cool~ Cool~{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.00,0:54:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.54,0:54:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, I fell asleep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.85,0:54:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't notice that you came in.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.95,0:54:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was because, because, of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.66,0:54:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, because of those islanders, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.63,0:54:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I got in this mess? \N- CEO, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.06,0:55:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this, this, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.33,0:55:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in their trap, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.80,0:55:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it even make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.14,0:55:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Act all innocent in the front,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.24,0:55:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the back, cheat like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.34,0:55:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.98,0:55:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.68,0:55:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to forgive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.60,0:55:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Secretary Tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.51,0:55:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.48,0:55:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.84,0:55:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? I came here to escort you.\NGive it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.95,0:55:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's ok. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.61,0:55:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.58,0:55:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you have to be used to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.29,0:55:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.89,0:55:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.42,0:56:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the restaurant doing fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.22,0:56:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, of course.\N- And is Miss Mi Sook doing well, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.96,0:56:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, yes.\N- Get in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.29,0:56:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in, get in,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.16,0:56:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.27,0:56:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.44,0:56:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The CEO is really busy today, so he couldn't come. \NContinue on getting in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.85,0:56:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.75,0:56:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was all my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.99,0:56:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"It happened because of my mistake. That's right."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.16,0:56:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"I should take responsibility."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.57,0:56:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.37,0:56:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've been unfairly cheated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.70,0:56:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for that medicine, if only not for that woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.64,0:56:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe she might be part of the plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.51,0:56:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be on the same team, same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.71,0:57:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Same team, same team.\N- You want to vent your anger on anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.15,0:57:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and you feel like you will explode right away if anyone touches you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.82,0:57:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.99,0:57:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. If I drink like a mad man
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.50,0:57:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and I work out 'till I feel like dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.77,0:57:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I sleep like a dead man, but after exactly 30 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.70,0:57:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my eyes open and
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.67,0:57:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.48,0:57:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hurts so much and the first thing that comes to my mind is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.31,0:57:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"I got married!"
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.38,0:57:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"I got married"...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.52,0:57:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.85,0:57:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I got married!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.32,0:57:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the thing that makes me so mad is
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.56,0:57:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.73,0:57:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to live my married life
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.73,0:57:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with that snail woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.80,0:57:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you mean by "snail"?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.50,0:57:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean the Mud Snail Bride (from Korean folk tale)?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.57,0:58:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, no, no not something good like that.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.58,0:58:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is about a terrifying snail that lives in Yeoul Island.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.71,0:58:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrifying snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.21,0:58:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are scared of snails? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.05,0:58:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing about snails is that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.79,0:58:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,they look innocent from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.06,0:58:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but their suction force is so strong. It's just incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.39,0:58:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get sucked by a snail,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.13,0:58:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that terrifying sucking feet,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.00,0:58:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}slowly, little-by-little, piece-by-piece,{\i}
